  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to provide continued supply of ruxolitinib alone, ruxolitinib
      plus background cancer therapy, or background cancer therapy alone to subjects from an
      Incyte-sponsored study of ruxolitinib that has reached its study objectives or has been
      terminated.

      This study will also provide another mechanism for reporting adverse events related to study
      drug safety.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
